articles.author: Ashish Dangwal
articles.title: F-16’s ‘Triumph’ Over Typhoon, Rafale Likely As Biden Urges Congressional Approval For Turkey’s Purchase - EurAsian Times
articles.description: Following a prolonged delay that even led to contemplation of acquiring Eurofighter Typhoons and Rafales, Turkey may soon secure the much-awaited green light from the US Congress to procure its desired F-16 fighter jets.
